## Change 1: inline Hann window

Replace `run_sysid.m:376`:

```matlab
w = hann(n);
```

with the symmetric Hann formula (matches `hann(n)` to FP precision):

```matlab
% Hann window (symmetric, equivalent to hann(n); inlined to avoid the
% Signal Processing Toolbox dependency)
if n == 1
    w = 1;
else
    w = 0.5 - 0.5*cos(2*pi*(0:n-1).'/(n-1));
end
```

The downstream amplitude correction (`mag = abs(Y(half, :)) * (2/sum(w))`) is unchanged — `sum(w)` is identical to `sum(hann(n))`.

