3. **Peak annotation present.** On a flown log with non-trivial vibration, the FFT figure should show 1-5 red triangles per axis with `<f> Hz / <amp>` labels at the dominant spectral peaks. For roll on a typical multirotor: expect a peak near the rotor blade-pass frequency (in the 30-50 Hz range typically) flagged.

